{"type": "article", "id": 14293, "title": "可弯折的创可贴", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-02T07:21:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000330hfWOrc72KNF5I8Yv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t普通的创可贴一旦贴在手指关节处，就难以弯曲手指，十分僵硬，很多时候没等伤口痊愈就把创可贴撕掉了。如果能将贴纸的中间掏空，使弯曲部位露出来，其实就能解决这个问题。简单的设计，你没想到吧。<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2015/09/01/bendy-wendy-bandaid/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141920JEgYaNwPjpIFZD2l.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"302\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.28761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141921AbLUaWJ3rY1OHG9V.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"443\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141921bkAShUtiuRPnjGMe.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"511\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141922NitmncjL6A1Gg0EM.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"510\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}